<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A boolean flag indicating whether the device is an active medical device (dependent on a source of energy)."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/isActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Is active"@en .
