<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A boolean flag indicating whether the device is intended to be partially or wholly introduced into the human body."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/isImplantable> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Is implantable"@en .
