# http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ActiveDevice
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ActiveDevice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
